race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Handicap (C1)
race.comment: Open race to close out the card. CHIEF IN CHARGE (1) goes well for hoop Guthmann-Chester who has a win and two placings from just three steers. Drawn to get a cosy run in transit from gate two and should play a major role in the outcome. DOMINANT DARCY (7) got the maiden out of the way here first-up and looks ready for the step-up to the 1350m journey now. In the mix. PROMINENT LAD (2) hails from an astute yard and gets 3kg off from the inside alley. Plenty to like about his prospects. BRUTAL LASS (15) strips fitter third-up from the break and gets in well at the weights with the 2kg claim. Might earn a cheque.
